---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy and Account Deletion for Departure: Fitness Quest">
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-12">Last updated: April 16, 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-text-muted text-[15px] leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            Qualia AI Consulting ("we," "our," or "us") operates the Departure: Fitness Quest mobile application
            (the "App"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information
            when you use our App.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">When you use Departure: Fitness Quest, we may collect the following information:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
            <li><strong class="text-text">Account Information:</strong> Your name and email address when you create an account.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-text">Fitness Data:</strong> Workout logs, exercise entries, sets, reps, weight, personal records, and training schedules that you input into the App.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-text">Photos:</strong> Selfies you voluntarily upload for our AI body transformation feature.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-text">User ID:</strong> A unique identifier for authentication and account management.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-text">Team Data:</strong> Team memberships, battle results, and team contributions.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Your data is used to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
            <li>Provide core app functionality including workout tracking, XP/rank progression, and personal records.</li>
            <li>Enable team features, leaderboards, and monster battle mechanics.</li>
            <li>Power AI image generation for the body transformation feature.</li>
            <li>Authenticate your account and maintain your session.</li>
            <li>Improve the App and develop new features.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">We use the following third-party services to operate the App:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
            <li><strong class="text-text">Supabase:</strong> For authentication, database storage, and file storage.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-text">Google Gemini API:</strong> For processing uploaded selfies to generate AI body transformation images.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-text">RevenueCat:</strong> For managing in-app purchases and subscriptions.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            These services have their own privacy policies governing their use of your data. We only share the minimum
            information necessary for these services to function.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Data Protection</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
            <li>We do <strong class="text-text">not</strong> sell your personal information to third parties.</li>
            <li>We do <strong class="text-text">not</strong> use your data for advertising purposes.</li>
            <li>We do <strong class="text-text">not</strong> share your data with third parties except as described above.</li>
            <li>All data is stored securely through Supabase's cloud infrastructure with row-level security policies.</li>
            <li>We implement technical safeguards to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your account and all associated data.</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent for photo uploads at any time by deleting your transformation images within the App.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Departure: Fitness Quest is intended for users aged 13 and older. We do not knowingly collect personal
            information from children under 13. If you believe we have inadvertently collected such information,
            please contact us and we will promptly delete it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes
            by posting the updated policy within the App or on this page. Your continued use of the App after
            changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Account Deletion -->
        <div class="border-t border-surface-light/50 pt-8 mt-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-6" id="account-deletion">Account Deletion</h2>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">How to Delete Your Account</h3>
            <p>
              To request deletion of your account and all associated data, email us at
              <a href="mailto:departure@engagequalia.com" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-light transition-colors">
                departure@engagequalia.com
              </a>
              with the email address associated with your account. We will process your request within 30 days.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">What Gets Deleted</h3>
            <p class="mb-3">Upon account deletion, the following data is permanently removed:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
              <li>Profile information (name, email, avatar)</li>
              <li>All workout logs and exercise entries</li>
              <li>Personal records and XP/rank progress</li>
              <li>All uploaded selfies and AI-generated transformation images</li>
              <li>Team memberships and battle history</li>
              <li>Equipment inventory and coin balance</li>
              <li>All in-app purchase records</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">Data Retention After Deletion</h3>
            <p>
              No personal data is retained after account deletion. The only exception is that anonymized
              team scores may remain in aggregate for other team members' historical records. This data
              cannot be linked back to your identity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <div class="border-t border-surface-light/50 pt-8 mt-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, your data, or account deletion, contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            <a href="mailto:departure@engagequalia.com" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-light transition-colors">
              departure@engagequalia.com
            </a>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm">Qualia AI Consulting</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
